Esp32 Wiring for the whole project

--------------------------------------
DHT22 Temperature and Humidity Sensor
-------------------------------------
GND (-) -> GND negative on esp32
VCC (+) -> 3.3v on esp32
OUT -> PIN 27
-------------------------------------

-------------------------------------
CAPACITIVE SOIL MOISTURE SENSOR
-------------------------------------
VCC (+) -> 3.3v
GND (-) -> GND
AOUT -> PIN 32
-------------------------------------

-------------------------------------
5v DC WATER PUMP & MOSFET & BATTERY
-------------------------------------
Battery's (+) -> VIN+
Battery's (-) -> VIN-

Pump's (+) -> OUT+
Pump's (-) -> OUT-

Mosfet's GND (-) -> GND
Mosfet's trig pin -> PIN 18
------------------------------------------------




